# đźŽŻ Sport & Health Marketplace - Core Rules

## Product Philosophy

**Always prioritize:**
- **MVP-first thinking**: Simple solutions over complex ones
- **Clean UX**: Mobile-friendly, clear hierarchy
- **Role separation**: Athlete, Coach, Admin (never break this)

**Never:**
- Over-engineer or add enterprise patterns prematurely
- Add features not explicitly requested
- Use hardcoded color values (hex) instead of design tokens

---

## Stack & Architecture

- **Framework**: Next.js 16 App Router
- **Backend**: Supabase (Auth, DB, RLS)
- **Auth**: Server-side `getCurrentUserWithProfile()`, `requireRole()`, helpers from `lib/authHelpers.ts`
- **Security**: RLS policies on all tables
- **Error Handling**: Error boundaries (`app/error.tsx`, `app/dashboard/error.tsx`) + structured errors (`lib/errors.ts`)
- **Logging**: Centralized logger (`lib/logger.ts`) - NO `console.log` in production

